text: The Tick Fire was a wildfire. It burned in Los Angeles County, California from October 24, 2019 to October 31, 2019. It burned several thousand acres. There was a mass evacuation of about 40,000 people from the Santa Clarita valley. ==References== Category:2019 in California Category:Santa Clara County, California Category:2019 fires Category:Fires in California Category:October 2019 events
